ma parte de tu vida.</p>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  <section class=\"py-28 px-8\" style=\"background-color:#F4F0EC;\" data-kid=\"217\">\n    <div class=\"reveal max-w-2xl mx-auto relative\" data-kid=\"218\">\n      <p class=\"text-xs font-600 tracking-[0.25em] uppercase mb-4\" style=\"color:#A45A52;\" data-kid=\"219\">No te pierdas nada</p>\n      <h2 class=\"font-serif-lora font-600\" style=\"color:#4B3621; font-size:clamp(2.2rem,4vw,3.4rem); line-height:1.05;\" data-kid=\"220\">Mantente conectado</h2>\n      <p class=\"mt-4 text-base\" style=\"color:#4B3621CC;\" data-kid=\"221\">Novedades, lanzamientos y ofertas pensadas para ti. Sin spam, lo prometemos.</p>\n\n      <div class=\"mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-end gap-6\" data-kid=\"222\">\n        <div class=\"relative flex-1\" data-kid=\"223\">\n          <input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"tu@correo.com\" class=\"w-full bg-transparent outline-none font-serif-lora text-xl pb-2 placeholder:text-[#4B362155]\" style=\"color:#4B3621;\" data-kid=\"224\">\n          <svg class=\"absolute left-0 -bottom-1 w-full\" height=\"12\" viewBox=\"0 0 400 12\" fill=\"none\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-kid=\"225\">\n            <path d=\"M2,7 C60,2 120,10 180,6 C250,1 320,11 398,5\" stroke=\"#A45A52\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" data-kid=\"226\"></path>\n          </svg>\n        </div>\n        <button class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-white text-sm font-600 shrink-0\" style=\"background-color:#A45A52; box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(164,90,82,.28);\" data-kid=\"227\">Suscribirse <i class=\"ti ti-send\" data-kid=\"228\"></i></button>\n      </div>\n\n      <p class=\"font-serif-lora italic text-right mt-12 text-lg\" style=\"color:#4B362199; transform:rotate(-3deg);\" data-kid=\"229\">Con cariño, el equipo Dimar</p>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  <footer style=\"background-color:#4B3621; color:#F4F0EC;\" data-kid=\"230\">\n    <div class=\"max-w-[1240px] mx-auto px-8 py-16\" data-kid=\"231\">\n      <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-12\" data-kid=\"232\">\n        <div class=\"lg:col-span-2\" data-kid=\"233\">\n          <p class=\"font-serif-lora text-3xl font-700\" data-kid=\"234\">Dimar</p>\n          <p class=\"mt-3 text-sm max-w-xs text-[#F4F0EC]/70\" data-kid=\"235\">Tu tienda online de confianza. Lima, Perú.</p>\n          <div class=\"mt-6 flex flex-col gap-2 text-sm text-[#F4F0EC]/70\" data-kid=\"236\">\n            <a href=\"mailto:contacto@dimar.pe\" class=\"flex items-center gap-2 hover:text-[#85B09A]\" data-kid=\"237\"><i class=\"ti ti-mail\" data-kid=\"238\"></i> contacto@dimar.pe</a>\n            <a href=\"tel:+51999999999\" class=\"flex items-center gap-2 hover:text-[#85B09A]\" data-kid=\"239\"><i class=\"ti ti-phone\" data-kid=\"240\"></i> +51 999 999 999</a>\n            <span class=\"flex items-center gap-2\" data-kid=\"241\"><i class=\"ti ti-map-pin\" data-kid=\"242\"></i> Lima, Perú</span>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"mt-6 flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"243\">\n            <a href=\"#\" aria-label=\"Facebook\" class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center border border-[#F4F0EC33] hover:border-[#85B09A] hover:text-[#85B09A]\" data-kid=\"244\"><i class=\"ti ti-brand-facebook\" data-kid=\"245\"></i></a>\n            <a href=\"#\" aria-label=\"Instagram\" class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center border border-[#F4F0EC33] hover:border-[#85B09A] hover:text-[#85B09A]\" data-kid=\"246\"><i class=\"ti ti-brand-instagram\" data-kid=\"247\"></i></a>\n            <a href=\"#\" aria-label=\"Twitter\" class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center border border-[#F4F0EC33] hover:border-[#85B09A] hover:text-[#85B09A]\" data-kid=\"248\"><i class=\"ti ti-brand-twitter\" data-kid=\"249\"></i></a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div data-kid=\"250\">\n          <p class